Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. This is it. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get us a drink, boss!
