Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty dependable guy, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who's pushing to do\Nthese dangerous stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a fine line between a\Ndaredevil and a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found a\Nbrutally murdered male body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units report to the scene at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty bad, l tell ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper unit is on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's the same as the\NBay Bridge incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There better not be another one\Ndoing stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!\Nlt feels great being near the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can smell the salty air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not here on vacation,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lighten up a bit. Don't be so uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Miko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing like a woman's crotch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm only letting you on site because\Nof direct orders from the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand that. And l don't\Nfind this one too interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say\Nit's part of our dirty business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. ln regard to that,\Nwe can clear it up by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, please rest assured that\Nl'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The damn politician's dumping\Nall over me on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, l've dispatched them to\Nthe Bay Area crime site.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means\Nhe's the only one not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mr. Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope you're not behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't have the kind of\Nartistic sense you see there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, are you telling me there's at\Nleast another responsible for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt looks like this is a job where\Nyou might have to risk your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can only wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're bringing down the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in touch with the chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! That body falls\Nunder our jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you touch it!
