Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Detective.\Nlt's just for a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so stiff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Ms. Takamizawa.\Nlt's in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's done, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just see how good\Nthey are at solving this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! You're too loud.\NWhat if someone hears you?
