Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! l don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so shocked.\NYou did that.
