Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...everyone calls me ''zombie\Nwoman'' behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
