Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes...!\Nlt feels so different this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time l came.
