Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how long does it\Ntake this drug to hit me?
