Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't pay for it.\Nlf it doesn't work, big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More! More! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill me too?!\NKoji! Please, no!
