Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person... lt's like\Nshe's calling out for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's suffering,\Nin very difficult circumstances.
