Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's the first time l felt\Nsomething when touching an object.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not sure myself\Nwhat to make of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touch it again!
