Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once more!\NPlease check it out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you listen!
