Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything about\Nthe human soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\Nl am a corpse after all!
