Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna go to the amusement park!\NYou too, right, big sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We're going to the\Namusement park then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn. So, l'm going to be\Nsurrounded by brats all day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim wasn't aware at all\Nthat he was in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assailant approached\Nfrom above...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where the victim wasn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either he has some superhuman power...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or perhaps he's able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim was taken by an enormous\Nforce that he couldn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was only able to flail his limbs\Nabout in futility.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assailant is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a bird? An animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he appears to be somewhat human...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the victim was dead before\Nhe had a chance to see his assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What he saw after that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an image of his own body\Nas he faced his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he was played with like a toy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:23:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l wonder how he felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look. There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not even a student but always\Nwondering around doing nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're a lot of\Nmen like that these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope he doesn't commit\Nsome weird crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.94,0:24:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to keep an\Neye on men like that.
