Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.38,0:24:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Yuta. Wow, what an\Namazing gun you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa bought it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.32,0:24:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? You sure have a\Ngood Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.73,0:24:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.13,0:24:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he always brings home\Nthe same toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.61,0:24:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! lt's Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.28,0:25:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm back, Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.45,0:25:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Yamada.\NOn your way home from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.79,0:25:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.16,0:25:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.13,0:25:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\Nl wanna hang out with Koji!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.46,0:25:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yuta. Don't be\Ndifficult on your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.75,0:25:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite some underwear\Nshe's got on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.92,0:25:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, you evil demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.62,0:25:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aghh! You got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.76,0:25:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yuta, he's a busy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.83,0:25:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, Mr. Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.53,0:25:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.50,0:25:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.84,0:26:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When l have a day off,\Nwe can spend more time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.27,0:26:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.28,0:26:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.08,0:26:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.35,0:26:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koji!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.05,0:26:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.02,0:26:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.99,0:26:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.46,0:26:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sure l locked the door though.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.23,0:26:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.10,0:26:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?\NSneaking into my place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.74,0:26:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lighten up. A pretty woman is\Nhere to see you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.77,0:26:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would be nice if you showed\Na little more enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.41,0:26:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't have much interest in\Nskanky bitches like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.48,0:26:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Now l know why you were\Ngetting excited by some housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.42,0:26:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l saw it, right through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.46,0:26:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently her husband's been\Nmissing for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.33,0:26:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.26,0:27:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you listen to the ladies talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.17,0:27:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can find out about\Neverything in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.84,0:27:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koji...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.30,0:27:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you have a chance,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.54,0:27:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's not at all the kind of\Nperson you think she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.94,0:27:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.28,0:27:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you one piece of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.85,0:27:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the ''natural'' types...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.99,0:27:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they're the ones you\Nhave to be most careful about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.66,0:27:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you strip her from that shell,\Nyou could be in for a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.76,0:27:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.99,0:27:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.70,0:27:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing\Nin my apartment anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.20,0:27:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got into a fight with my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.44,0:27:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can l spend just one night here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.71,0:27:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you let me stay, then\Nl'll let you have me just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.31,0:27:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd wanna do it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.11,0:27:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.59,0:27:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease me. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.00,0:28:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.53,0:28:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.55,0:28:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on your knees, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.20,0:29:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsy-daisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.98,0:29:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.01,0:29:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.41,0:30:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't sleep very well unless l do\Na handstand before l go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.78,0:30:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty different.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.05,0:30:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.15,0:30:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The walls are thin in this place,\Nso keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.59,0:30:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest hurts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.90,0:30:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.61,0:30:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tomorrow will be all lovey dovey.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.38,0:30:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.69,0:30:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong will power.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.37,0:31:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it, Koji?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.11,0:31:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have your period?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.98,0:31:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.38,0:31:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l should be getting it any day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.12,0:31:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l smell blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.42,0:31:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then that's a problem.\Nl don't have any tampons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.49,0:31:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a drag. l just got it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.46,0:31:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.94,0:31:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Koji?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.61,0:31:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.51,0:31:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.61,0:31:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.34,0:31:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know you wanna do it, there's\Nno need to get all freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.31,0:31:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l told you that at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.38,0:31:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.02,0:31:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd do it with you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.46,0:31:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this stench of blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.70,0:32:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's as if there's blood\Nsplattering all over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.51,0:32:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.41,0:32:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.13,0:32:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The multiple murders must be his doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.63,0:32:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.67,0:32:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in touch with everyone!\Nl'll try to hold him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.24,0:32:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.09,0:34:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an emergency!\NEveryone, please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.42,0:34:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster possibly the multiple\Nmurderer sighted near Koji's!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.56,0:34:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going after the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.50,0:34:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, head over to the site!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.11,0:34:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's finally started.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.05,0:34:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lsn't this just\Nwhat we were hoping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.42,0:34:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one or the other will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.72,0:34:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.89,0:34:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise there's no way of\Nknowing who's stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.74,0:34:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.44,0:35:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll set up a great stage\Njust for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.70,0:35:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.35,0:36:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.38,0:36:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You just watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.70,0:36:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's strong...!
